td.div: Nederlands: Vlag van Suriname van 1959 tot 1975.

English: Flag of Suriname, constituent country of the Kingdom of the Netherlands (1954-1974), from its adoption in 1959 until the achievement of independence on 25 November 1975, on which date the flag was changed to its current form.
Français : Drapeau de la Guyane néerlandaise (1959–1975).
